data.description: Looking for a large home with plenty of acreage? Don't miss out on this Spacious four-bedroom, two-bathroom home on 4.5 acres of land with numerous updates! This beautiful property features a new roof, new AC and heater for year-round comfort. Enjoy the open kitchen which boast a brand new kitchen sink and a large pantry! Also, don't forget to check out the direct access to the backyard from your Primary bedroom. With two living rooms, a dining room, and a versatile playroom/sunroom, you'll have plenty of space to entertain and relax. Additionally, this property includes a camper shed, a two-car carport, and an enclosed two-car garage. The washer and dryer are included, and you'll have peace of mind with a home warranty. The yard is partially fenced, offering privacy and space for outdoor activities. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity!
